; Regression test for issue #655: Ledger no longer downloads stock prices using the -Q option (BZ#655)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/655
;
; The -Q flag (alias for --download) should be recognized and should fall back
; to price database entries when the getquote script fails or is unavailable.

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00

2024/01/01 Buy stock
    Assets:Investments    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

test -V bal Assets:Investments
            $1500.00  Assets:Investments
end test
